## Push Summary — skrptiq-cli (main)

### What shipped — GH#440 standalone distribution

- Version management with build-time ldflags
- .gitignore
- GitHub Actions CI workflow (checkout both repos, build/test/vet)
- GitHub Actions release workflow (5 platform binaries on tag push)
- curl installer script (scripts/install.sh)
- Release script with --help (scripts/release.sh)
- Token fallback for cross-repo access

### To trigger first release
1. Set ENGINE_ACCESS_TOKEN secret (or enable org cross-repo access)
2. Run: ./scripts/release.sh
